{"meta":{"domain":"subjects","kid":"5197","authors":[{"fullname":"Nicolas Tournadre","id":"6"}],"title":"","dates":{"created_at":"2013-09-15 04:15:37 UTC","updated_at":"2013-09-15 04:15:37 UTC"}},"nodes":[{"index":0,"parent_index":-1,"body":"<p class=\"Paragraph\">A distinction may be made between expressions of situation, of existence, and of possession.<\/p><p class=\"Paragraph\">The verb \u201cto be\u201d in the sense of \u201cto be located at\u201d (situational sense) is translated by the future of the verb \u201cto stay\u201d <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f56\u0f66\u0fa1\u0f51\u0f0b<\/span>, or its honorific form<span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"> \u0f56\u0f5e\u0f74\u0f42\u0f66\u0f0b<\/span>:<\/p><ul> <li><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f44\u0f0b\u0f53\u0f44\u0f0b\u0f63\u0f0b\u0f56\u0f66\u0fa1\u0f51\u0f0b\u0f40\u0fb1\u0f72\u0f0b\u0f61\u0f72\u0f53\u0f0d<\/span> \u201cI shall be (or stay) at home.\u201d<\/li> <li><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f41\u0f7c\u0f44\u0f0b\u0f62\u0f92\u0fb1\u0f63\u0f0b\u0f66\u0f62\u0f0b\u0f42\u0f5e\u0f74\u0f42\u0f66\u0f0b\u0f40\u0fb1\u0f72\u0f0b\u0f62\u0f7a\u0f51\u0f0d <\/span>\u201cHe will be (or stay) in the capital.\u201d<\/li> <\/ul><p class=\"Paragraph\">Possession and existence are expressed by using the future form of the verb <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f61\u0f7c\u0f44\u0f0b<\/span>:<\/p><ul> <li><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f58\u0f7c\u0f0b\u0f63\u0f0b\u0f58\u0f5a\u0f7a\u0f0b\u0f58\u0f0b\u0f61\u0f7c\u0f44\u0f0b\u0f42\u0f72\u0f0b\u0f62\u0f7a\u0f51\u0f0d <\/span>\u201cShe will have twins.\u201d<\/li> <li><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f41\u0f7c\u0f44\u0f0b\u0f63\u0f0b\u0f51\u0f44\u0f74\u0f63\u0f0b\u0f61\u0f7c\u0f44\u0f0b\u0f42\u0f72\u0f0b\u0f62\u0f7a\u0f51\u0f0d <\/span>\u201cHe will have money.\u201d<\/li> <\/ul><p><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f62\u0f99\u0f7c\u0f42\u0f0b\u0f41\u0fb2\u0f0b\u0f61\u0f7c\u0f44\u0f0b\u0f42\u0f72\u0f0b\u0f58\u0f0b\u0f62\u0f7a\u0f51\u0f0d<\/span> \u201cHe won\u2019t have any problems.\u201d<\/p>","title":""}]}